    "In the framework of applications for smart buildings, transfer learning ensures excellent performance in the knowledge sharing of ML-based model employed for emulating building dynamics (Grubinger et al. 2017; Pinto et al. 2022b), load forecasting (Li et al. 2021; Li et al. 2022), occupancy detection (Mosaico et al. 2019), activity recognition (Chiang et al. 2017) and Fault Detection and Diagnosis (FDD) (Li et al. 2023)."
